port back to [Syra](https:\/\/mapgenie.io\/gothic-1-remake\/maps\/valley-of-mines?locationIds=603976)\n\n**Reward:**\n- 100 XP - after convincing Seraphia\n- 100 XP - after convincing Velaya\n- 500 XP\n\n\n**Notes:**\n- **BUG** Completing [The Great Awakening](https:\/\/mapgenie.io\/gothic-1-remake\/maps\/valley-of-mines?locationIds=607873) Quest will fail this Quest\n- Currently, the quest is bugged, and it's tricky to finish it if NOT a part of the Old Camp\n- The Transform into Meatbug spell can be used to get past the guards into the main castle building to talk to Velaya and Seraphia\n- Suggest a way around for this quest if there are any other options :-)","latitude":"0.78491855118084","longitude":"-0.71544170379613","features":null,"ign_page_id":null,"tags":[],"media":[]},{"id":610571,"map_id":945,"region_id":null,"category_id":15875,"title":"Joining the Warders","description":"**Chapter 3**\n\n**IMPORTANT NOTE:** It is impossible to be a [Warder](https:\/\/mapgenie.io\/gothic-1-remake\/maps\/valley-of-mines?locationIds=610571) and a [Fire Mage](https:\/\/mapgenie.io\/gothic-1-remake\/maps\/valley-of-mines?locationIds=889976) at the same time!\n\n**How to Start:** Talk to [Thorus](https:\/\/mapgenie.io\/gothic-1-remake\/maps\/valley-of-mines?locationIds=595406) about becoming a Warder after finishing [The Brotherhood's Plan](https:\/\/mapgenie.io\/gothic-1-remake\/maps\/valley-of-mines?locationIds=607201) Quest\n\n**Quest Steps:**\n- Take 3 Diggers and escort them to the Exchange Zone\n- Meet with [Kirgo in the Exchange Zone](https:\/\/mapgenie.io\/gothic-1-remake\/maps\/valley-of-mines?locationIds=892651) and help him defend the site\n- Report back to [Thorus](https:\/\/mapgenie.io\/gothic-1-remake\/maps\/valley-of-mines?locationIds=595406)\n\n**Reward:**\n- 700 XP\n- [Warder's Armor](https:\/\/mapgenie.io\/gothic-1-remake\/maps\/valley-of-mines?locationIds=610572)","latitude":"0.79189699830923","longitude":"-0.71028649806999","features":null,"ign_page_id":n